Comment: There will be no more action in this match as the referee signals full time.
The foul by Robert Snodgrass (West Ham) is worthy of a card and a yellow is duly shown by Michael Dean.
The resulting corner from Willian (Chelsea) is cleared.

Ross Barkley (Chelsea) receives a clever pass and shoots from mid-range. His shot looks like it's going in the bottom right corner, but Lukasz Fabianski has other ideas and makes a brilliant save. Chelsea force their opponents to concede a corner.
We will have 4 min. of added time.
